summary: This is a small island mod that is currently a WIP. The inner island ring is the most complete area and the outer ring is there but is mostly bare.
descriptionHtml:
The island is based around the idea of a volcano that had it's magma chamber emptied by the Red mountain hundreds of years before it's eruption. This caused the structure to collapse into the emptied chamber and develop the two rings of land.

The cliffs will remain steep around the inner shores but I will improve the slope to allow easier exit in most areas. There are only a few NPCs (First time use of a navmesh) and a few interior cells to buildings on the inner island.

The door to Felgol is in Dragonsreach on the second level balcony. Please leave all followers in Skyrim until further noticeÂ
author: Mitchmander
